data.description: TWO LIVING AREAS, TWO BEDROOMS, PLUS AN ADDITIONAL BONUS ROOM THAT COULD BE USED AS A THIRD BEDROOM OR OFFICE SPACE!!! Coziness and character abound in this beautiful 1948 vintage home. With lots of the original charm preserved, the current owner’s tasteful updates have added tremendous value to the property, the half/shower has been meticulously rebuilt from the sub-floor up and the HVAC was replaced in 2019. Solar system paid off by seller. New state-of-the-art windows throughout installed in 2022. Matching Quartz kitchen countertops and backsplash hood installed in 2023.Bedrooms have exquisite crown and baseboard molding plus built in bookshelves fronting accent-wall made from antebellum mansion. State of the art Security System. Home is just minutes from downtown, Penn Square Mall, I-44, and easy access to just about anything you could think up. Come see this one today!
